Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems you still haven't grasped the situation, but I'm doing this as a favor for you and your daughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,With just a phone call right now, I could make this all go away as if it never happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.22,0:00:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.58,0:00:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I could make it so you never see your daughter again, and during this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.92,0:00:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been thinking about what I should do. Now it's clear.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,For Minji,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.10,0:00:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I will remove you.
